HEADWORD: Goltschut
<hw>Golt"schut</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A small
ingot of gold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A silver ingot, used in Japan as money.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

